reviewText:
I don't know why anybody would spend over $30 on this when you can get this and 19 others for the same price or less.  Warriors of the Wasteland is an unapologetic Italian nod to Mad Max and Road Warrior.

Fred Williamson, fresh from other B movies is billed here but the true stars are the cars and their Ulta Special sound effects as they are driven.  My gosh, a little bit of that noise goes a VERY long way.
